26TH OCTOBER 1944 28TH FEBRUARY 2003
"Remember me when I am gone away"
The strength of your love and the sound of your
laughter will live in our hearts forever"ط
صWALTER LEARY
17th Feb.1920 - 23rd Dec.1994
COUNCILLOR ST.KATHERINE'S WARD 1964-1985
